Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.11,0:05:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响  真美来帮你抓住它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.41,0:05:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快出来吧  我会道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  那里有什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  有蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪…哪里  蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:23.05,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  真…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:28.68,Bann,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(418,0)\pos(495,0)\1c&E7DCD2&\3c&FFFFFF&}萩原雪步\N765事务所所属偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟑螂在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.27,0:05:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪步怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:36.02,Bann,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(418,0)\pos(130,0)\1c&3396F4&\3c&FFFFFF&}高槻弥生\N765事务所所属偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:39.40,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}雪步请冷静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.32,0:05:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁快来把蟑螂…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪步  不能在茶水间地板上挖洞呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是快点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把蟑螂…  快把蟑螂从这里赶走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  哈姆藏是仓鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:05:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈姆藏？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上当了吧  真
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊织你又来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上当的人自己笨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  真  伊织
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在拍你们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视台的采访…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.28,0:06:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  这是有在拍摄的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  要早点说呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是水濑伊织  请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:39.38,Bann,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(417,0)\pos(130,0)\1c&E196FC&\3c&FFFFFF&}水濑伊织\N765事务所所属偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈姆藏  你已经被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投降出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  哈姆藏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.73,0:06:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  那么吵闹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是热闹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个要多少钱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.81,0:07:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据容量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据大小不同价格不同吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.91,0:07:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.94,0:07:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(240,350)}这是算小的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(480,350)}容量是指记忆体…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.18,0:07:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好复杂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的  连我也会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:23.29,Bann,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(417,0)\pos(130,0)\1c&D35C23&\3c&FFFFFF&}如月千早\N765事务所所属偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.01,0:07:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  化妆占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个月的工作运只有一星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是恋爱运有三星呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:40.06,Bann,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(417,0)\pos(130,0)\1c&C03493&\3c&FFFFFF&}三浦梓\N765事务所所属偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可思议的占卜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的会准吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.82,0:07:47.07,Bann,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(417,0)\pos(495,0)\1c&670EA5&\3c&FFFFFF&}四条贵音\N765事务所所属偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:49.24,fad1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「相信占卜吗？」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  如果写的是好事的话就相信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵音的占卜呢  怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:07:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我坚信人生是靠自己去开拓命运的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运是靠开拓出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是这样呢  贵音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:10.84,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}哈姆藏你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:12.18,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}好像进这里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.68,0:08:13.93,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}乖乖束手就擒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然跑到美希美希的那里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈姆藏也是男生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！  哈姆藏真H！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈姆藏！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了哈姆藏的食物真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:35.12,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}美希美希  摄像机哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.12,0:08:36.99,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}快说点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星井美希  初中三年级
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:46.75,Bann,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(417,0)\pos(135,0)\1c&42DFB0&\3c&FFFFFF&}星井美希\N765事务所所属偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  就这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太短了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有胸部很大哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.64,0:08:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  美希美希
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:09:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱睡的孩子长得大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这里人手不足
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  没听清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请再重复一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  大家给我适可而止！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:21.54,fad1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,350)\fad(500,501)}职业：
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:21.54,fad1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,350)\fad(500,501)}偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:29.04,frz,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz270\pos(190,180)\fad(501,0)}歌唱课程\N(星井·天海·如月)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呀  虽然还有很多不明白的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是觉得一点点慢慢来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.99,0:09:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希做得不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:58.03,frz,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz270\pos(190,200)\fad(0,0)}杂志采访「月刊偶像」\N(菊地·萩原)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:10:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我对体力很有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想把舞蹈磨练得更好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想在电视里的歌唱节目
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者大舞台上帅气地跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菊地君在女生中很有人气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.76,0:10:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为假小子的关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成这样都是爸爸害的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:26.89,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}因为他不让打扮得像个女生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天要突破爸爸那堵墙！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着吧  爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  萩原雪步小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不擅长和男性说话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么要成为偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.75,0:10:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我几乎没什么值得骄傲的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却想成为偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  是不是太天真了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你问我…  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:11:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想改掉畏缩的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.85,0:11:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是朋友又去帮我申请了面试…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我还是不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个我听不清你在说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂雪步  快回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.78,0:11:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:18.20,frz,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz270\pos(400,200)\fad(0,0)}CD大街贩卖&握手\N「太阳的嫉妒」(天海)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.78,0:11:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是天海春香  请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  律子小姐忙不过来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:30.46,fad1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(0,0)}音无小鸟  765事务所员工
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就像这样来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,300)}给  请看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:34.88,fad1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「就像是兼任制作人吗？」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底只是帮忙而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.13,0:11:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  我该去下个地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摄影师先生  春香就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:49.89,fad1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「哎…！？」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:53.31,fad1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「拜托了是…」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,300)}被拜托了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:55.86,fad1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「哈…」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,300)}那就一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.57,0:11:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:00.99,fad1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「噢  噢…」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:03.12,frz,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz270\pos(190,170)\fad(0,0)}CHEX  LIVE  垫场\N15点入场  （如月）
Comment: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=========================
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:09.37,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(208,209)}蒼い鳥　もし幸せ近く…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:09.37,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(208,209)}青鸟  如果幸福就在附近…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=========================
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:18.01,fad1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「对唱歌有什么想法吗？」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是什么样的歌曲  都想要认真对待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.14,0:12:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不这样的话  对歌和对听众都会很失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:30.85,fad1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「真的很喜欢唱歌呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,300)}是的  我只有唱歌了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以没时间玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.99,0:12:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经可以了吗  我想要集中下精神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我那样跳出去  还叫着「等下！」
